      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm flying into heathrow tomorrow and need to get to edinburgh. i was thinking of taking the heathrow express to paddington then switching to an lner train. how much buffer time should i actually leave between getting off the express and catching the lner so i don't miss it? thanks",
